{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Random Stuff About Stuff","author":"David Kerwick"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"d13cd226-e00f-5ca8-870c-e9c64e7c561e","excerpt":"When converting legacy apps to bring them up to Java 8 one of the things I sometimes run into is when switching from Date to LocalDate that some jps’s that…","html":"<p>When converting legacy apps to bring them up to Java 8 one of the things I sometimes run into is when switching from Date to LocalDate that some jps’s that format dates.</p>\n<p>You may get the error</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token class-name\">Caused</span> by<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> javax<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>el<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token class-name\">ELException</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Cannot</span> convert <span class=\"token number\">2014</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">08</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">12</span>T12<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">39</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">08</span> of type <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> java<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>time<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token class-name\">LocalDateTime</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">to</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> java<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>util<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Date</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>The jstl tags don’t know how to directly handle java 8’s LocalDate and LocalDateTime\nSo what you’ll need to do it parse in like a String first and then use that value for the formatting so something like</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token namespace\">fmt:</span>parseDate</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>${patient.dob}<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">pattern</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>yyyy-MM-dd<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">var</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>patientDob<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>date<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token namespace\">fmt:</span>formatDate</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">pattern</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>dd/MMM/yyyy<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>${patientDob}<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Dealing with Java 8 LocalDate in jsp's","date":"January 17, 2018"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/2018-01-17-dealing-with-java-8-localdate-in-jsp-s/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2018-01-17-cntlm-and-mac-startup/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CNTLM and Mac startup"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/new-mac-install/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"New Mac Install"}}}}